Package org.biopax.paxtools.model.level2

package org.biopax.paxtools.model.level2
This package contains the interfaces that maps to the BioPAX level 2 specification. Note that although BioPAX level 2 is not camel case we have opted to use the capitalization style directly to avoid any confusions.
